{"tid":1603690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其他國家革命成功係因為肯升級","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:24:17.000Z","uid":141330,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a949acc0711bec925c0f819d8be70e9bb79894fe","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:42:25.000Z","msg":"宜家聽得最多係<br />\n邊度邊度有幾隻狗 棄gear<br />\n但係諗深一層 最近肯即時跟隊打波既人冇一百都幾十<br />\n呢個時世真係好需要快閃版復仇者聯盟<br />\n無論黨鐵站 定係狗屋<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為佢地除咗件衫 <br />\n出到街笑笑口你地就當佢地係普通人<br />\n狗無一個係無辜啊！ 佢地著起gear就濫殺市民！<br />\n<br />\n佢地越冇gear/得幾個 先越容易帶到恐懼比佢地<br />\n恐怖唔應該只係降臨喺市民身上<br />\n<br />\n組團打波！"},{"pid":"ab347f147d79769d271ef8a822e47032c62cc8f9","tid":1603690,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"無示威嗰陣埋伏夠屋同宿舍放魔法"},{"pid":"c6605bff1de8af0b17adabf1d045fb7cf3f447b1","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab347f147d79769d271ef8a822e47032c62cc8f9","tid":1603690,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"無示威嗰陣埋伏夠屋同宿舍放魔法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e6eebe1f93438e0b893ae8e04d9ab3c024ae84","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"對家著起件衫 乜撚都唔驚 <br />\n手段越做越撚痴線<br />\n我地首要條件係 要令佢地感到恐懼<br />\n驚咗自己個身份"},{"pid":"77869ae0b0ca7758c58138877d72d3513e1bf7e7","tid":1603690,"uid":326930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"係要升級呀！！！！<br />\n其實今日啲狗都有升級左啦，<br />\n<br />\n開槍（tg以外）爽手左好多，已經去到完全零制度啦，打人打得更兇狠、更明目張膽，警察通例已經於2019年9月29號完全廢除。<br />\n<br />\nPs. tg已經唔算係槍，狗認為係極低武力，同 狗 隻 對 住 燈 柱 屙 尿 是 同級別武力。"},{"pid":"06af4ff77aa959bab7052898261fccf9e3fe48cf","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T02:07:37.000Z","msg":"人地都越黎越猖狂 我地點可以放鬆啊"},{"pid":"afff692b536f57d732cb1520ac1aecddeec69d2a","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d30a3b0021584995b4f1ff0478d14a8ea8ff58","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc376a3ca419b4eb47a9a2450cb151cd85331b","tid":1603690,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:12:47.000Z","msg":"大家會進化, 而且進化速度好快"},{"pid":"c2ee7b021d455e575097664d909c3798fbc7de9e","tid":1603690,"uid":141330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}